\SE[2]...Hey, sis. \!\SE[3]If we keep going like this, won't
that kid become a criminal accomplice to us?

\SE[0]As for us, it would be easier if that child took the
blame for us...

\SE[50]Sigh, I guess there's no helping it. \SE[3]I'll make
it look convincing, so follow my lead. You're good at that
kind of thing, right?

\SE[2]Huh? Aren't you moving forward? Is something wrong
with both of you?
\SE[2]According to the information, it should be... right?

\SE[4]Alright? Laura, \SE[3]if someone asks you Why are you
in a place like this? \SE[4]from now on...

\SE[38]I was forcibly brought here as a hostage by that
woman! \SE[3]Answer like that. Got it?

\SE[3]Here, let's practice. \.\SE[4]Why are you in a place
like this?

\SE[38]I was forcibly brought here as a hostage by that
woman! \!\SE[3]...See, let's do it again.
\SE[4]Why are you in a place like this?

\SE[99]Um... \SE[19]I was forcibly brought here as a hostage
by that woman.

\SE[7]That's good. Try putting a little more emotion into
it. \SE[4]Why are you in a place like this?

\SE[102]I was forcibly brought here as a hostage by that
woman!

\SE[24]That's good! Let's say it one more time at the end.
\SE[4]Why are you in a place like this?

\SM[double]\SE[33]I was forcibly brought here as a hostage
by that woman!!

\SE[72]Perfect! I think you're doing a pretty good job, you
know?
Who are you!! \!How did you infiltrate here!!

\SE[22]Stop! \SE[19]If you want to protect the safety of the
civilians, don't move a single step!

Kuh... How cowardly! \!An escaped prisoner! Call for
reinforcements!!

\SE[19]...As expected, the odds are not in our favor with
this number of people.

They're... they're not here! \!Don't let them escape!! Chase
them! \.Chase them!!
Why are you in a place like this?

\SM[double]\SE[33]I was forcibly brought here as a hostage
by that woman!!

\SE[17] (I unintentionally showed the results of my
training...)

I see... Poor thing. \!You're safe now, so take a rest in
the back.\. It's best to rest for a bit.

Not here. Hurry, to Luna's place...!
